rComments: Dr. K is the most helpful professor I've ever had. She will make suggestions for what to look for if you're stuck and will provide extra background material for you to read. She lets you know exactly where you can improve and uses a rubric when grading. She seems stern at first but wants to see you do well as long as you put forth the effort.
teacherRatingTags: ['Caring', 'Gives good feedback', "Skip class? You won't pass."]
